          <actionDate>2018-10-19</actionDate>
          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>50 Votes for the Wall Act </b></p> <p>This bill establishes the Border Wall and Security Trust Fund for funds appropriated to construct a wall (including physical barriers and associated detection technology, roads, and lighting) along the international border between the United States and Mexico by January 19, 2021. </p> <p>The bill provides appropriations to the fund equal to amounts requested by the Department of Homeland Security, which may not exceed a total of $25 billion. </p> <p>The authority provided by this bill terminates on September 30, 2028. When the authority expires, any unobligated balances in the fund must be returned to the Treasury. </p>]]></text>
        </item>
